data.description: Prime Pocono! From its location in a wooded community, to excellent proximity to major Pocono attractions, this property meets all demands for home, vacation, or investment! A contemporary design offers for a dramatic façade and presentation as you enter a soaring open-concept living space, cathedral ceilings and skylights offering openness while a wood-burning fireplace maintains the warmth and coziness desired. This gathering area presents ample room for a living space, dining, and free flow with the open kitchen. Behind, an enclosed porch offers space to appreciate the natural surroundings in addition to a side rear covered deck. The main level also features a spacious bedroom and full, updated bath with laundry facility! Upstairs you will find a loft space overlooking the great room below and a hall with clerestory windows allowing for ample light and space! A second full, updated bath serves the upper level’s two generous bedrooms, as well as a convenient hall linen closet. Throughout the home you will find new flooring and paint, giving this retreat a fresh feeling, as well as peace of mind with a new roof and freshly painted exterior! Don’t miss your opportunity to see this lovely Pocono home!
